#: contents/ui/ConfigVoice.qml:720
msgid "Repair Engine"
msgstr "Reparación de motor"

#: contents/ui/ConfigVoice.qml:736
msgid ""
"Check validates folders, microphone, audio output, and required packages. "
"Repair Engine appears only when package support is missing or broken."
msgstr ""
"Verificar valida carpetas, micrófono, salida de audio y paquetes requeridos."
" Repair Engine aparece solo cuando falta o está roto el soporte del paquete."

